    [dl('Spend/activity data + supplier PCF data (Pathfinder)', 'Category emissions calculation', 'S3 emissions by category with PCAF DQ scores'), dl('Reduction lever library (sector, category specific)', 'Reduction pathway modelling', 'Abatement potential by lever and adoption timeline'), dl('SBTi validation criteria by category', 'Target alignment check', 'Proposed S3 target vs SBTi coverage and ambition requirements')],
    'Required for SBTi Scope 3 target setting (67% coverage), CDP leadership band, and CSRD ESRS E1 upstream/downstream disclosure. Pathfinder Framework integration enables industry-leading PCF precision for Cat 1 purchased goods.'
