      'NREL — 2022 Offshore Wind Energy Cost Analysis Report',
      'BNEF — Offshore Wind Market Outlook 2024 — Costs, Finance and Policy',
      'EU Taxonomy Technical Expert Group — Offshore Wind Technical Screening Criteria',
